
{ Resize an image

Change width to 400 pixels:
code {
convert in.jpg 400 out.jpg
code }

Change height to 300 pixels:
code {
convert in.jpg x300 out.jpg
code }

At most 400x300, keeping aspect ratio
code {
convert in.jpg 400x300 out.jpg
code }

  
Force specific size
code {
convert in.jpg 400x300! out.jpg
code }



}
